 1992-06131992-03-260,  IA&ND,  ,  , 
PrecisRe-appointment of Stindar K. Lal, of Toronto, Ontario, as Chairman of the Arbitration Board for a term of three years, effective January 27, 1992; re-appointment of Alfred Ernest Pallister, of Edmonton, Alberta, as Vice-Chairman of the Arbitration Board for a term of three years, effective January 27, 1992; and appointment of John Parker, of Sidney, British Columbia and Jim Bourque, of Yellowknife, Northwest Territories, as members of the Arbitration Board for a term of three years.
